com.hannesdorfmann.mosby.mvp.delegate

Interface MvpDelegateCallback<V extends MvpView,P extends MvpPresenter<V>>

  • Type Parameters:
    V - The type of MvpView
    P - The type of MvpPresenter
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    MvpViewStateDelegateCallback<V,P>, MvpViewStateViewGroupDelegateCallback<V,P>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Dagger1MvpActivity, Dagger1MvpFragment, Dagger1MvpLceActivity, Dagger1MvpLceFragment, Dagger1MvpLceViewStateActivity, Dagger1MvpLceViewStateFragment, Dagger1MvpViewStateActivity, Dagger1MvpViewStateFragment, MvpActivity, MvpFragment, MvpFrameLayout, MvpLceActivity, MvpLceFragment, MvpLceViewStateActivity, MvpLceViewStateFragment, MvpLinearLayout, MvpRelativeLayout, MvpViewStateActivity, MvpViewStateFragment, MvpViewStateFrameLayout, MvpViewStateLinearLayout, MvpViewStateRelativeLayout

    public interface MvpDelegateCallback<V extends MvpView,P extends MvpPresenter<V>>
    The MvpDelegate callback that will be called from ActivityMvpDelegate or FragmentMvpDelegate or ViewGroupMvpDelegate. This interface must be implemented by all Activity, Fragment or android.view.View that you want to support mosbys mvp.y
    Since:
    1.1.0
